<br>
Team points don't mean jack crap to me.  They are in no way an indication of anything, they don't decide who is winning, levels and zones decide that. <br>
<br>
Personal points don't mean anything either.  They go to the person that tries to exploit the system the most.   Generally lead by solo pkers that go around looking for afk people, naked people or people low on health.<br>
<br>
Guild points don't mean a whole lot either, but at least they are an indication of which guilds are out there pking.  <br>
<br>
<br>
If you can't see how bad the point system is something is seriously wrong with you.  Yes its how verant rates who is winning the server, but it certainly doesn't mean anything.  Your goal in the game should be to have fun, control territory and kill the other teams.  You shouldn't be concerned with the points more than anything else.  The first time a groupmate gates because he doesn't want to lose points on a posible too low green that is attack us,  I'm going to scream.  I'd rather see them do away with points than leave it broken the way it is now. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=2428.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=2428.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=2428.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=2428.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=2428.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=2428.topic&start=121&stop=128>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessage?topicID=2780.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showMessage?topicID=2774.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.threadControl?topicID=2428.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsu